PresentationObject.Note:
When the message content is collapse the subject line is cropped using the ellipsis e.g.

"this is a long subject textual line from the bank" becomes "this is a long..."

 

when we expand the message we also want to be able to see the full subject line - the function defined in here accomplishes that and it is called from the Show Info ClassToggler widget

Attribute.name: Text
Attribute.original:
<script>
function expandEllipsis(data)
{
	var mainDetails = $('#'+data.IdToUpdate).prev("div[class*='MainDetails']", "div[class*='MainDetailsOff']");
	mainDetails.toggleClass("MainDetailsOff").toggleClass("MainDetails");
	var subject = mainDetails.find("span[class='longellipsis'],span[class='longellipsisOff']");
	subject.toggleClass("longellipsisOff").toggleClass("longellipsis");
}
</script>
